name: Children of the Damned
description:
After MVDRA and SVNYA experimented with a growing embryo. They protect the embryo day by day until the embryo finds its true form. However, bad things happen. A deviant son born to this world, dazed and confused. He suddenly broke his egg with unusual power, and try to attack MVDRA and SVNYA. This child, Children of the Damned.
